Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.79,0:01:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(187,216)\fs16\fad(600,600)}暑假结束\N\N\N\N\N在众多比赛中获胜的“秋名86”之名\N\N\N\N传遍了区内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.29,0:02:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,219)\fs15\fad(600,600)}须藤京一率领LAN EVO军团“Emperor”\N\N\N\N在激烈的缠斗之后将妙义最快的\N\N\N“Night Kids”打败了\N\N\N\N就在高调征服群马地区的狼烟燃起不久之时...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.73,0:02:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 这个弯转得太马虎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.72,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时你应该会选更严格的路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.46,0:02:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏离了十五厘米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真子的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是碓冰最快的蓝色Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“Impact Blue”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.29,0:03:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像真子啊 必须再专心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.18,0:03:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn隶书\fs25\fad(1100,1700)\c&HF11F53&}在冲击之蓝的彼方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.01,0:03:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 还有这样的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.13,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说你被那个叫池谷的人甩了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪 我就觉得跑法很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是那种精神状态会直接表现在驾驶上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的感觉派吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.43,0:04:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着池谷 恋慕就是要包容对方的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.29,0:04:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 赶快去约定的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后再教训你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.49,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八点在初次和池谷先生相遇的招牌下等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.83,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子一直都是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我...而我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.14,0:05:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个大混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.19,0:05:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脚开始痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌凉鞋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 求求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.01,0:05:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再给我一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.58,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堵车?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.16,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不穿凉鞋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.88,0:06:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是想不通啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.37,0:06:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然也会被甩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是他黏着你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.42,0:06:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有什么误会吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样想过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那以后也一直等待着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.14,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没来过电话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不你打打看?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.98,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能那么纠缠不休呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.05,0:06:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过了约定时间还等了三小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方毫无回应 也就是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我没兴趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.13,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你是真的喜欢他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.43,0:07:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连驾驶都受影响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得即使献给他也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,献什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,处女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.01,0:07:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道你是成熟还是大胆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可那男人好在哪里呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.72,0:07:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诚实 温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一谈到车...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会很投入 不知不觉就忘了时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 什么? 慎吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.73,0:08:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪 其实...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? LAN EVO军团去了妙义?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.51,0:08:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 听说了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.82,0:08:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枥木车牌的LAN EVO出现在了妙义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.58,0:08:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Kids被干掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中里那笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然输给外地人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些人的真面目已确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长是须藤京一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以日光伊吕波坡道为主赛道的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.61,0:08:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.24,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么企图?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 慎吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.25,0:09:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过Night Kids还真惨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就是这么无情的问候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.37,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是沙雪 我的老相识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.99,0:09:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.42,0:09:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时跑的就是这家伙 叫中里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来到底怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主场居然会输掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.72,0:09:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群马的堡垒由我来守护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.92,0:09:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你们的企图打落妙义谷底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.26,0:10:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没理由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还有机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我阻止不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.75,0:10:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有谁能阻止他们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.12,0:11:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对手是叫Emperor 清一色LAN EVO的车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.58,0:11:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在毅上山赛输给REDSUNS不久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没走出这个打击的阴影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶节奏有点混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.01,0:11:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是属于跑法起伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不住压力的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不想被你说成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是...还没人能将32驾驭得这么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.63,0:11:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这附近地区开32的人里应该是NO.1吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能把毅和32甩开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那LAN EVO快得离谱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.22,0:11:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说过要在一个月内踏平群马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心啊 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.53,0:11:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为妙义和碓冰近在咫尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好 求之不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.31,0:12:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们这碓冰最快的“Impact Blue”可不是白叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好强硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.75,0:12:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想说得太难听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.23,0:12:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好别管这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思? 慎吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是我一开始就没有胜算?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...不是这个意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆乳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别小看女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管谁来我们都不会逃避的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.55,0:12:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说的就这些?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那疯丫头是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.91,0:12:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么后果我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毅 特地带你来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.64,0:12:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是要提醒沙雪当心Emperor的厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么都不说话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.74,0:13:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在听吗? 毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.29,0:13:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆乳...厉害...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.19,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之Emperor的LAN EVO车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像要对群马地区发起攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这事我也听说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消息传得沸沸扬扬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.94,0:13:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Kids的贴纸也被一切为二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.06,0:13:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒贴在了尾翼上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.59,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要这样做吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.16,0:13:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们真的会来这儿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.41,0:13:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来的话怎么办? 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是兵来将挡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.09,0:13:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管对手是谁我们都会迎战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.86,0:13:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是碓冰最快的“Impact Blue”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么决定了 大家听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.60,0:13:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.35,0:14:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有类似LAN EVO的车来了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上打我手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.61,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之后过了两天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LAN EVO还没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.95,0:14:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定不会来这边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.04,0:14:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话也能松口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子状态也不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在比赛的话能否发挥自己最好水平...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.89,0:14:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.81,0:15:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这种混乱的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都要摆脱出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.08,0:15:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想忘掉池谷的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.07,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会出现在我家浴室啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是悠闲洗澡的时候 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.53,0:15:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来接你的 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.70,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走到哪儿去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.32,0:15:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碓冰山道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LAN EVO出现啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.30,0:15:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别慢吞吞的 穿好内裤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.77,0:15:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等 真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.12,0:16:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是LAN EVO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.00,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有错 是Emperor
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联系沙雪她们了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.33,0:16:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? LAN EVO来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你说的Emperor
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.63,0:16:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在赶去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.96,0:16:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.82,0:16:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LAN EVO军团出现在碓冰山道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.49,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吗? 毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.18,0:17:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里也都是FR的漂移小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.49,0:17:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,群马地区水平也不怎么样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.71,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回去向京一报告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:17:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老兄们 想比赛就来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.15,0:18:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里我们的Sil-80是最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.25,0:18:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慎吾 你和那Sil-80其中的一个女人什么关系?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说沙雪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.67,0:18:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么样 青梅竹马而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从小学到中学都是同一所学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住得也很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.73,0:18:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道...毅...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那种类型?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.13,0:18:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正是个倔强的疯丫头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.28,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不是那种听得进别人忠告的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算她们的Sil-80是碓冰最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.56,0:18:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与LAN EVO比赛也毫无胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耍漂移的技术确实厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.52,0:19:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在当地或许不会输给任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在比纯粹速度时的严谨操控上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们几乎毫无经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.89,0:19:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操控起来像在玩游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.07,0:19:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会出现一些天真的跑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以正规的四驱为对手是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.94,0:19:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也明白 毅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.42,0:19:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想说“因为女人所以慢”这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沙雪她们毫无胜算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是Sil-80啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.52,0:19:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且车手还是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺有趣的样子 就陪你玩玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样自作主张没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.61,0:19:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是来侦查的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.44,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后被京一臭骂我可不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.51,0:19:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么死板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们特意跑这么远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微玩一下也不会惩罚我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要赢了就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.57,0:20:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可万一有什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 会有万一吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以这种恬噪的女人为对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的EVO IV怎么会输?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吧 真子 干掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们犯了我们的禁忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.69,0:20:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小看女人的家伙最让我生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.08,0:20:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好 鼓起干劲上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.69,0:20:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子的眼神变凌厉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.06,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时的真子很快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.25,0:20:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是个情绪决定速度的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下山一轮定胜负 碓冰的路很窄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以用先行后追的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.39,0:21:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先行者将后追者甩开就算赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.13,0:21:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法甩开的话再互换位置 直到决出胜负为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个比法如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你选哪个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.03,0:21:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最初的位置由你决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.54,0:21:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 第一轮我后追
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.61,0:21:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我在后面欣赏屁股吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.02,0:21:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧 过了第一个弯就会全力加速冲刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.48,0:21:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是比赛开始的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.69,0:21:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我说几遍?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.75,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在Emperor里也算是佼佼者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对女人开的Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.29,0:21:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的EVO IV是百分之二百不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.18,0:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.96,0:22:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能输给小看女车手的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.89,0:22:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 鼓足干劲了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.25,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.96,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.24,0:22:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.04,0:22:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EVO IV不可能输给Sil-80的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.42,0:22:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.10,0:22:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关键时刻还是女人比较有胆色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能赢吗? 对手可是打败了Night Kids的Emperor
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.72,0:23:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大马力涡轮的四驱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.99,0:23:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人早就退缩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.37,0:23:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可沙雪她们赢不了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.18,0:23:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没人能赢了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.83,0:23:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她们是碓冰最快的Impact Blue
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.83,0:23:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能相信她们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.64,0:23:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这一带沙雪她们的蓝色Sil-80是最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.49,0:23:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.32,0:23:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是本地车手 跑得不赖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.36,0:23:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有对向车 尽情地漂移过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.66,0:24:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这EVO IV的漂移和FR的小伎俩不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.25,0:24:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开足引擎 高速入弯才是四驱漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.19,0:24:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 感觉不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.37,0:24:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下个弯 紧贴内线抓地过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.84,0:24:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠着岩壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.63,0:24:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前是势均力敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.46,0:24:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能咬得住呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.37,0:24:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不太清楚是因为EVO IV的性能还是技术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.29,0:24:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确像你说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.37,0:24:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂移是玩耍的成分居多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.23,0:24:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是轮胎的使用方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.74,0:25:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上次看Sil-80跑是什么时候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.83,0:25:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天时吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.85,0:25:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那或许已经有所改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.00,0:25:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也曾经历过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.21,0:25:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在某处经受洗礼觉醒的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.73,0:25:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有能力的人就会产生巨变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.12,0:25:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上也有像秋名86那样的FR车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.16,0:25:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能胜过四驱的FR也是存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:28.54,0:25:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那86是独一无二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.69,0:25:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沙雪她们有机会看一次86的跑法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.72,0:25:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就另当别论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.86,0:25:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人还这么狂妄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.18,0:25:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不能输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.85,0:26:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 真子的跑法和以前不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.21,0:26:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打方向明显变得精细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.25,0:26:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种驾驶方式的印象...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.26,0:26:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多半是来自与秋名86的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.61,0:26:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子觉醒了 好厉害 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:33.59,0:26:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场比赛赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.39,0:26:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后面的EVO IV在弯道跟不住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:58.58,0:27:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的身手没想像中厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.13,0:27:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多半不是那个在妙义击败Night Kids的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.19,0:27:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 老是让他在后面看着也很不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.75,0:27:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接着的C=121分胜负吧 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.72,0:27:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你也知道 今天在直路的跑法不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.13,0:27:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要比平时更高的速度入弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.58,0:27:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要操控得恰如其分哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:35.07,0:27:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 没有对向车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:37.75,0:27:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.28,0:27:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种连女人都能过的弯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.89,0:27:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的EVO没理由不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.56,0:28:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 挤不出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:13.40,0:28:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的路线过不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.49,0:28:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.71,0:28:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.46,0:28:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事绝不能让京一知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.64,0:29:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:13.31,0:29:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LAN EVO军团呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.57,0:29:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 慎吾 已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.36,0:29:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:26.37,0:29:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.93,0:29:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别灰心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.76,0:29:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是在主场输掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.36,0:29:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.18,0:29:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.16,0:29:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们赢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.35,0:29:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赢了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.30,0:29:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子太厉害啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.28,0:29:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是天才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:55.00,0:29:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.17,0:29:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.41,0:30:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 慎吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.80,0:30:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是特地来替你们助威的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.86,0:30:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那辆Sil-80散发着难以形容的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.94,0:30:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是真材实料的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.73,0:30:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子果然厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.82,0:30:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是昨天的LAN EVO车手不怎么样吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.24,0:30:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 那家伙身手相当好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.72,0:30:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是输给秋名86之前的我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:58.56,0:31:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定会是场苦战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.63,0:31:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那以后精细地打方向盘就成了主题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.66,0:31:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天赢得漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.33,0:31:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但决定胜败的C=121
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.90,0:31:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却成了充满表演性的华丽漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.30,0:31:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里我总会有难以想像的斗志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.12,0:31:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来仍会不寒而栗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.93,0:31:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏你还笑得出来 真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.31,0:31:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还以为会死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.57,0:31:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 你完全成了感觉派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:38.41,0:31:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一受到某些影响就会突然改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.13,0:31:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉心情舒畅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.87,0:31:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可前路漫漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.71,0:32:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总想去追逐那蓝天遥远彼端的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.82,0:32:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时用不着男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.34,0:32:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走着瞧 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.95,0:32:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,池谷前辈你感冒了? 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.14,0:32:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.31,0:32:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点摇晃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:39.70,0:32:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 昨天下的雪留在路上结冰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.82,0:32:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没无钉防滑胎果然不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.55,0:33:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那车怎么回事? 明明没装无钉防滑胎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.10,0:33:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.87,0:33:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.76,0:33:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险 危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.21,0:33:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.93,0:33:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开 让开 右边 右边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:31.31,0:33:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.49,0:33:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.34,0:33:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摔死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:36.84,0:33:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.64,0:33:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn隶书\fs25\fad(700,900)}多愁善感的白色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.94,0:34:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真气人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:01.54,0:34:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一起开始玩滑雪板的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:03.73,0:34:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有你滑得那么好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.14,0:34:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.54,0:34:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没有哪个女孩的运动神经能及得上你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:13.89,0:34:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始漂移时也这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:16.48,0:34:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是感觉好 很快就上手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:25.17,0:34:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 这不是慎吾吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:28.47,0:34:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:30.43,0:34:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 这种地方也能碰到 太巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:34.81,0:34:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也玩滑雪板?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:39.53,0:34:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.28,0:34:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.28,0:34:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会玩滑雪板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:49.14,0:34:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来慎吾他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.31,0:34:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小学时经常流鼻涕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.06,0:34:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:55.38,0:34:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就被戏称为“流鼻涕的慎吾”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.35,0:35:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此成了个“下流”的车手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.56,0:35:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪 别乱说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:05.49,0:35:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时不是碰巧感冒了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:11.23,0:35:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 真子 你想去滑雪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:15.01,0:35:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 我要和慎吾聊聊往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.31,0:35:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位先生能陪她去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:24.51,0:35:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:27.17,0:35:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:29.63,0:35:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.64,0:35:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.18,0:35:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不太靠得住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.16,0:35:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过作为你的朋友算是正经的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.56,0:35:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赛车方面怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.51,0:35:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Kids里属于挺快的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.88,0:35:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然赢不了碓冰最快的Impact Blue啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.10,0:35:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 她那么可爱居然没男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.26,0:36:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就毛遂自荐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:03.37,0:36:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢? 怎么能介绍给你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.39,0:36:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 慎吾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:08.64,0:36:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让她发现这是相亲哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.00,0:36:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漏馅的话真子会生气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.37,0:36:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.38,0:36:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是沙雪你又如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.67,0:36:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.77,0:36:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前的中里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.05,0:36:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙似乎很相得中你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:49.21,0:36:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑得很好啊 玩滑雪板几年了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:51.98,0:36:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年开始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.10,0:36:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:54.84,0:36:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没见过能在这么难的场地滑得如此顺畅的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.21,0:37:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩起来既兴奋又快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.01,0:37:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一入了迷就会特别专心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.76,0:37:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 白天慎吾的朋友你觉得怎样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:25.98,0:37:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问我觉得怎样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.49,0:37:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉人还不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:30.98,0:37:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺老实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.77,0:37:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.97,0:37:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.43,0:37:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面也不太了解啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:41.45,0:37:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来有戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.55,0:37:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 我听到件让我有点挂心的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.61,0:37:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,REDSUNS的高桥凉介...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:52.23,0:37:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拉秋名86去组建新车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.98,0:38:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是专为县外远征特设的车队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.63,0:38:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗? 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.35,0:38:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种想法真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:08.70,0:38:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的脚步不会停留在一个地方 总是不断前进呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:15.62,0:38:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是一群了不起的人 虽然不甘心...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.13,0:38:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却不得不承认是真正的领袖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.37,0:38:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想再见一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.27,0:38:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓海过得好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.30,0:38:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子肯定变得更帅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.93,0:38:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼光不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.08,0:38:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙雪真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.92,0:38:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉燃烧起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.00,0:38:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 去滑雪场中途的道路感觉不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.68,0:38:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山下也没有雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.18,0:38:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想到一块儿去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.52,0:38:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.76,0:38:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还真是乐此不疲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:05.85,0:39:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.15,0:39:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山道都是雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.27,0:39:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启介 能征服冬天的人也能征服夏天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.18,0:39:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的计划将在春天起动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.98,0:39:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 冬天傻呆着是不会进步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.46,0:39:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去雪地跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:29.87,0:39:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在结冰而溜滑的路面上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.87,0:39:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑中完全空白拼命地跑就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.96,0:39:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天换上高抓地力轮胎后就会明显见效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.81,0:39:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会磨炼得焕然一新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.71,0:39:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑法会像经受过暴风雨的洗礼一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.91,0:39:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,启介 我们要在各地的山道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:56.11,0:39:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下谁都破不了的赛道纪录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:58.91,0:40:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,创造出传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.42,0:40:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪并不是妨碍 而是最好的训练伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.43,0:40:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车手是不分季节的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.41,0:40:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无钉防滑胎抓地力不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.20,0:40:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的训练才有效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:28.43,0:40:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见到弯道就要拿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.15,0:40:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是车手的本能吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.52,0:40:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那车怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.45,0:40:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.14,0:40:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从哪儿来的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.32,0:40:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.72,0:40:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.75,0:40:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是同一类型的中速弯道 很无聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:58.19,0:41:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是碓冰最棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.29,0:41:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 慎吾啊 什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.52,0:41:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两人经常见面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.84,0:41:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很起劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:19.98,0:41:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像也在约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:22.52,0:41:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.90,0:41:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.29,0:41:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节也快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.86,0:41:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:38.39,0:41:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子终于要告别二十年的单身生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.33,0:41:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SW20真是辆好车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.62,0:41:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉不错 但双人座还是不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.23,0:41:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我想换辆更实用的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.96,0:42:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像四驱的旅行车之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.70,0:42:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要放弃做车手?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.88,0:42:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.72,0:42:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是找借口 但我已充分享受过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:19.52,0:42:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技术还很差时 不顾一切不断地练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.95,0:42:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道自己在不断进步时非常开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:28.68,0:42:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可到了某个程度后就能看清前路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.92,0:42:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了目标后热情也慢慢消退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.15,0:42:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉就会渡过这个阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.02,0:42:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.96,0:42:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...目标...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.45,0:42:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不会这么简单就失去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.92,0:42:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想过在今年夏天引退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:56.24,0:42:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.05,0:43:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在有机会见识了水平比自己高得多的跑法后...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.87,0:43:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得自己还是太肤浅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:07.85,0:43:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可做不到这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:10.82,0:43:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我并不是以职业车手为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.85,0:43:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想...可以的话...希望真子也放弃赛车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.41,0:43:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑山道会有危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:42.13,0:43:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你毕竟还是个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:45.31,0:43:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一出事故的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.69,0:43:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 谁都无权剥夺别人做自己喜欢的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:53.28,0:43:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果是真子的男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.65,0:44:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会放任自己的恋人每晚都去跑山道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:06.50,0:44:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为会担心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:09.97,0:44:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了赛车 这世上还有很多有趣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.20,0:44:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在明朗的日子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.20,0:44:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打扮漂亮出来的话不是更适合吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.42,0:44:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为真子很可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:37.74,0:44:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子 我是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.39,0:44:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没这么喜欢过一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:45.60,0:44:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:12.23,0:45:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:15.25,0:45:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很开心你能这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:22.72,0:45:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我们刚认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:27.08,0:45:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然说这种事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:33.44,0:45:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用现在就答复的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:37.38,0:45:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一星期后的圣诞节再见面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.70,0:45:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前能好好考虑一下吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.12,0:46:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快活得很啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.55,0:46:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节有什么节目?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.45,0:46:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊 没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.96,0:46:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,池谷 你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:09.57,0:46:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.43,0:46:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是孤独车手吧 树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.16,0:46:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.49,0:46:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们太凄惨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.15,0:46:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一脸心事重重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:32.30,0:46:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.83,0:46:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想跟沙雪说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.65,0:46:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.51,0:46:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这独自承担的习惯可不太好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.10,0:46:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要考虑的事很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.68,0:46:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如为了什么目标而跑...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.90,0:46:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前都没认真地讨论过这个话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.87,0:47:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是莫名地以提高水平为目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.96,0:47:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旁人看来是不是很奇怪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.53,0:47:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪 一点也不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:10.28,0:47:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被洗脑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.61,0:47:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子真的太天真了 轻易就受到了影响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:21.06,0:47:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管别人怎么说 我们还是我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:29.27,0:47:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:08.87,0:48:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.28,0:48:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:12.41,0:48:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平安夜把你叫到这种地方来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:17.42,0:48:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.50,0:48:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:23.49,0:48:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.78,0:48:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和你比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:28.02,0:48:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.86,0:48:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你坐在我旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:41.93,0:48:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时一定是沙雪在那里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:47.21,0:48:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:51.01,0:48:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:25.60,0:49:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害 不 是可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:27.86,0:49:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:47.76,0:49:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊真子 远超我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:50.98,0:49:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Night Kids里能开到这样的也不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:54.59,0:49:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定还在毅和慎吾之上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:01.09,0:50:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得能理解你让我坐上去的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.19,0:50:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的答复吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:11.21,0:50:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 这是我自己的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:17.10,0:50:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人说是笨女人也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:20.28,0:50:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法舍弃倾注在赛车上的这股热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.11,0:50:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后我仍想继续追赶跑在我前面的人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:36.39,0:50:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使追不上 这一刻我也要把目光投向同一个方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:42.70,0:50:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:44.62,0:50:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.37,0:50:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.44,0:50:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:11.55,0:51:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:14.10,0:51:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可被真子所思慕着的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.69,0:51:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在真的妒嫉死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.68,0:51:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拓海怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.27,0:51:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道在约会?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:32.95,0:51:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的事鬼才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:36.51,0:51:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们自己来庆祝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:41.93,0:51:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:43.53,0:51:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤独车手万岁 万岁 万岁
